=Wenzhi (Tom) Fang （方文智）

~~~
{}{img_left}{./photos/u.jpg}{alt text}{162}{220}{}
Hello and welcome! I am currently a final-year master advised by Prof. [https://faculty.sist.shanghaitech.edu.cn/faculty/zhouyong/index.html Yong Zhou] and [https://shiyuanming.github.io/ Yuanming Shi] at [https://www.shanghaitech.edu.cn ShanghaiTech University], majoring in Information and Communication Engineering. Earlier, I obtained my bachelor’s degree in Communication Engineering from Shanghai University in 2020.



#My research interest lies in the intersection of machine learning and communication networks, in particular federated learning, optimization as well as their applications to 6G, IoT and AI.


You can find my CV [./photos/CV_fangwenzhi.pdf here].

