== News

*I am currently searching for Ph. D. position (2023 Fall). If you are interested in working with me, please feel free to contact me！*

== Research
My research interests include 
- Distributed Optimization.
- Wireless Communication, Signal Processing.
- Machine Learning, Federated Learning.

#[research.html Find out more].
